					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You'd need maybe a 64-entry cosine table, but then you'd need to multiply that by the speed to get the rectangular velocity. An 8-bit by 8-bit multiply takes a scanline and a half unless you do it through a quarter square lookup table.</div>

